                    <span>This book is definitally my favorite book ever! I have loved elephants for a long time. I thought that I had no intrest in non-fiction books until I read this book. I started renting it from the library, and I continued to rent it until I was more than half way through the book. At that point my dad bought it off amazon.com. This book is full of facinating facts on elephants, and the writers, Oria Hamilton and Iain Douglas are two favorite non-fiction authors. Iain Douglas has made me want to be an elephant biologist. The book is almost like a fiction book in that it is so exciting.</span>
                  
              
